lead_paragraph: Pregnant women should consider not traveling to the 2016 Olympic Games in Brazil due to the risk of Zika virus infection, the U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: CDC Cautions Pregnant Women Against Travel to Rio Olympics
